Package handlers

Class MultiPlayer

java.lang.Object
handlers.MultiPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameConstants, PathConstants
public class MultiPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements PathConstants, GameConstants
The MultiPlayer class is responsible for handling actions made on the MultiPlayer UI, as well as starting the server and clients. It handles choices made by the host such as the map choice or number of lives, and then communicates these choices with the server.
